</h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-102_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Child protection in early years and childcare settings is a fundamental responsibility that requires vigilance, knowledge, and proactive measures. By adhering to statutory requirements, implementing best practices, and fostering a culture of continuous improvement, early years practitioners can significantly contribute to the safety and wellbeing of children.
